  基于电感耦合等离子体质谱(ICP-MS)法同时测定玛卡中16种稀土元素
   Simultaneous Determination of 16 Rare Earth Elements in Maka by Inductively Coupled Plasma Mass Spec-trometry (ICP-MS)
 
